<i>adjective</i>: 입바르다 [입빠르다], 격의없다 [겨긔업따/겨기업따] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adjective</i><br>
<dt>입바르다 [입빠르다]</dt><br>
<dd>unreserved; straightforward; outspoken</dd><br>
<dd>바른말을 하는 데 막힘이 없다.</dd><br>
<dd>Not hesitating in speaking right words.</dd><br>
<dt>격의없다 [겨긔업따/겨기업따]</dt><br>
<dd>frank; candid; unreserved; open</dd><br>
<dd>서로 생각을 솔직히 이야기할 정도로 매우 친밀하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Being on close terms with someone to the point that one can express one's opinions frankly.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>